thread.title: C Jayasuriya
thread.title_full: Ticketmaster Resale reviewed by C Jayasuriya

author: C Jayasuriya
title: C Jayasuriya
text:
I used the Ticketmaster Resale site to grab two last minute tickets since to the cricket @ Geelong a few weeks ago. The Ticketmaster site didn't have any tickets, so paid a higher price through their resale site for the tickets.
I was dumbfounded to see that many vacant seats on the day though. Yes it was cold, there was rain around, but, to see that many vacant seats made me think "someone's making a good dollar here, is that legal" ?
